Guys get excited because HUGE things are happening in the baby world! 👏

As a crunchy mom, I was thrilled to see more brands choosing better materials at the @theabcshow 

✅ Organic cotton clothing, bedding & more
✅ Less plastic = more glass + stainless steel
✅ More flame retardant free car seats + strollers 
✅ More furniture with low VOCs 

Bigger brands are launching some really new, exciting products as well as entire new lines + emerging brands are bringing totally new concepts to the table! 

